# Telegram Configuration
# Instructions:
# 1. Create a Telegram Bot with @BotFather on Telegram
# 2. Get your BOT_TOKEN from @BotFather
# 3. Create a Telegram group for your security staff
# 4. Add the bot to the group with Admin permissions
# 5. Get the GROUP_ID by:
#    - Enable group members to see who added the bot
#    - Use a bot helper to retrieve the group ID
#    - Or send a message and check logs
# 
# Example format: TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=123456789:ABCDEfghIjklmnopQRSTuvwxyz1234567890
# Example format: TELEGRAM_GROUP_ID=-1001234567890

TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=8707040896:AAGN5dk9eM4xrXezBRknRW8DFqVncBLHI8E
TELEGRAM_GROUP_ID=-1003897474155

# LLM Configuration (Groq)
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# Other Services
# Add other environment variables here as needed
